@UnaNancyOwen, the problem has been addressed in [2.14.0](https://github.com/IntelRealSense/librealsense/releases/tag/2.14.0), along with significant refactoring of pipeline request resolution. In particular, `enable_all` / default `start` for recordings will always select all recorded streams. We hope the new solution will offer more consistent and predictable behavior. 
Thank you for reporting this issue. 
If you have any problem with the new solution please open new issue (and reference this one).

